---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import '../styles/index.css';
---
<Base
  title="AXON Studio — Visual IDE for Physiological Closed-Loop Control"
  description="Visual programming language design suite, built from the ground up to eliminate the friction of setting up physiological control pipelines, leaving only the science."
>

<script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
  "name": "AXON Studio",
  "url": "https://runaxon.com",
  "description": "A visual IDE for physiological closed-loop control and simulation pipelines.",
  "applicationCategory": "ScientificApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Web",
  "offers": {
    "@type": "Offer",
    "price": "0",
    "priceCurrency": "USD",
    "description": "Sign up for early access"
  },
  "provider": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "AXON",
    "url": "https://runaxon.com"
  }
}
</script>

<nav>
  <div class="container">
    <a class="logo" href="/">AXON</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/learn">Learn</a>
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/VTzvfPuc" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta">Discord</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">AXON Studio</p>
      <h1>A Visual IDE for<br><em>Physiological Closed-Loop</em><br>Control and Simulation</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        AXON Studio is a hand-crafted design environment that eliminates the friction of PCLC development.
        With a native visual simulation language, a physiological model builder, and modern control theory templates, 
        you can <span style="color: #d3869b">skip to the interesting parts.</span></p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="#waitlist" class="btn btn-primary">Request Early Access</a>
        <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-secondary">See How It Works</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="screenshot-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="screenshot-wrapper">
        <div class="screenshot-label">AXON | Studio</div>
        <img
          src="/images/landing/landing-page-1.png"
          style="border-radius: 10px"
          alt="AXON Studio plant builder showing a Schnider pharmacokinetic compartment model with auto-generated Python code"
          class="screenshot"
          loading="eager"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="how" id="how-it-works">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color:#f0f0f0">From diagram to simulation in minutes.</h2>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">01</span>
          <div>
            <p class="step-title">Build your model graphically</p>
            <p>Drag compartments onto the canvas and connect them with flux arrows. AXON Studio knows the semantics of physiological systems, so the code is automatically generated.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">02</span>
          <div>
            <p class="step-title">Simulations run at maximum speed</p>
            <p>Under the hood, the Myelin engine translates your code into C, enabling the fastest simulations possible.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-num">03</span>
          <div>
            <p class="step-title">Close the loop and optimize</p>
            <p>Wire in a controller block, attach an evaluator, and run your closed-loop pipeline. Tune controller parameters manually or let the optimizer search the parameter space automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color:#f0f0f0">Features</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <p class="card-icon">[ PLANT BUILDER ]</p>
          <p class="card-title">Visual Compartment Modeling</p>
          <p>Draw multi-compartment PK/PD models on a canvas. Real compartment, input, clearance, and virtual compartment primitives. Code is generated as you build.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="card-icon">[ MYELIN ]</p>
          <p class="card-title">Python → C Transpilation</p>
          <p>Myelin compiles your simulation blocks to C and validates the output against the Python reference — fast execution without sacrificing correctness.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="card-icon">[ CONTROLLER ]</p>
          <p class="card-title">Closed-Loop Controller Design</p>
          <p>Connect a controller block to your plant. Wire in measurements and actions. Build PID, MPC, or custom controllers in the same visual environment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="card-icon">[ OPTIMIZER ]</p>
          <p class="card-title">Automated Parameter Search</p>
          <p>Define a parameter space and an evaluator. Let AXON search for optimal controller parameters across your closed-loop pipeline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="card-icon">[ SCENARIO LOADER ]</p>
          <p class="card-title">Scenario Configuration</p>
          <p>Configure simulation parameters and set the initial state of your plant. Define the conditions your pipeline runs under before a single step is simulated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <p class="card-icon">[ PATIENT LOADER ]</p>
          <p class="card-title">Patient & Cohort Modeling</p>
          <p>Translate patient demographics and clinical parameters into initial plant states. Run your pipeline across an entire cohort without manual state initialization.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="audience">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 style="color:#f0f0f0">Who It's For</h2>
      <div class="audience-grid">
        <div class="audience-item">
          <svg class="audience-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
            <path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/>
          </svg>
          <strong>Industry</strong>
          <span>Design, simulate, and optimize physiological closed-loop control systems in a purpose-built visual environment.</span>
        </div>
        <div class="audience-item">
          <svg class="audience-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M9 3h6M9 3v7L5 20h14L15 10V3"/>
            <path d="M7 16h10"/>
          </svg>
          <strong>Academia</strong>
          <span>Learn physiological modeling and closed-loop control through hands-on simulation — without getting lost in implementation details.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="waitlist" id="waitlist">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Early Access</p>
      <h2 style="color:#f0f0f0">Get early access to AXON Studio.</h2>
      <p class="section-sub">AXON Studio is under active development.<br>Join the Discord to follow along and get download instructions.</p>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/VTzvfPuc" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary discord-btn">Join the Discord</a>
      <p class="form-note" style="margin-top:1.25rem">Prefer email? Reach out at <a href="mailto:anthony@runaxon.com" style="color:var(--accent)">anthony@runaxon.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <span>AXON © 2026</span>
    <span>Visual IDE for physiological closed-loop control.</span>
  </div>
</footer>
</Base>
